<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Recuperar palavra-passe — GamiBook</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f3f7f8; font-family: 'Manrope', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .card { width: 100% !important; border-radius: 0 !important; }
      .body-pad { padding: 28px 20px !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f3f7f8;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="background-color:#f3f7f8;padding:40px 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table class="card" width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation"
          style="width:560px;background:#ffffff;border:2px solid #1a262e;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:5px 5px 0 #7fb8b4;">

          <!-- Cabecalho -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#7fb8b4;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;padding:28px 40px;text-align:center;border-bottom:2px solid #1a262e;">
                            <span style="font-family:'Outfit','Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#1a262e;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">GamiBook</span>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Corpo -->
          <tr>
            <td class="body-pad" style="padding:40px 40px 32px;">
              <h1 style="font-family:'Outfit','Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#1a262e;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.3px;">
                Recuperar palavra-passe
              </h1>
              <p style="font-size:15px;color:#34434d;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 12px;">Olá!</p>
              <p style="font-size:15px;color:#34434d;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 28px;">
                Recebemos um pedido para redefinir a palavra-passe da tua conta GamiBook. Clica no botao abaixo para escolheres uma nova palavra-passe.
              </p>

              <!-- Botao neo-brutalista: camada exterior = cor sombra (#7fb8b4), padding dir+baixo deixa sombra visivel -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin:0 0 32px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#7fb8b4;border-radius:12px;">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:0 4px 6px 0;">
                          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                            <tr>
                              <td style="background:#4e9d98;border:2px solid #1a262e;border-radius:12px;">
                                <a href="{{ url }}"
                                  style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Outfit','Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.2px;">
                                  Redefinir palavra-passe
                                </a>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Divider -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="100%" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
                <tr><td style="height:2px;background:#e4eef0;border-radius:999px;"></td></tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Link alternativo -->
              <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#52656f;margin:0 0 6px;">
                Se o botao nao funcionar, copia este link para o browser:
              </p>
              <p style="font-size:12px;color:#2e7f7b;word-break:break-all;margin:0;">{{ url }}</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Aviso -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 40px 32px;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#f3f7f8;border:2px solid #e4eef0;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;">
                    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#52656f;margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
                      O link e valido durante <strong style="color:#1a262e;">7 dias</strong>. Se nao pediste a recuperacao da palavra-passe, ignora este email — a tua conta esta segura.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Rodape -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#f3f7f8;border-top:2px solid #1a262e;border-radius:0 0 14px 14px;padding:20px 40px;text-align:center;">
              <p style="font-size:12px;color:#52656f;margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
                &copy; 2026 GamiBook &nbsp;·&nbsp; Plataforma de leitura gamificada
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
